@startuml Quick Typer Game - System Context

!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Context.puml

LAYOUT_WITH_LEGEND()

title C4 Level 1: System Context Diagram

Person(player, "Player", "User yang bermain game typing")
Person(admin, "Administrator", "User yang mengelola konten game")

System(quickTyper, "Quick Typer Game System", "Platform game mengetik untuk meningkatkan typing speed dan accuracy")

Rel(player, quickTyper, "Bermain game, melihat leaderboard", "HTTPS/JSON")
Rel(admin, quickTyper, "Mengelola stages, phrases, themes", "HTTPS/JSON")

note right of quickTyper
  **Core Features:**
  - User authentication & authorization
  - Stage & phrase management
  - Typing game dengan scoring system
  - Leaderboard per stage
  - Multiple attempts allowed
  
  **Key Metrics:**
  - Typing speed (WPM)
  - Accuracy (%)
  - Score dengan bonuses & penalties
  
  **Deployment:**
  - Containerized (Docker)
  - API Server (Go)
  - PostgreSQL Database
end note

@enduml

